## Key Differences from Current Output

| Current (bad) | Should be (good) |
|---|---|
| Every chapter starts by attacking Glock | Each chapter starts with WHAT MAKES THIS GUN UNIQUE |
| Spec dump: weight, capacity, trigger, price every time | Only specs relevant to THIS gun's selling point |
| "Humilla a Glock", "paliza", "ladrillo" | Fair comparison: "Glock gives you X, this gives you Y" |
| "After 5000 rounds no failures" (fabricated?) | "The manufacturer claims X. In our data, Y" |
| Same formula × 8 chapters | Each chapter structured around a DIFFERENT lead angle |
| No testing context | "At 25 yards, off a bench rest, with Federal 124gr" |
| Generic "it's great for everyone" | "If you carry appendix in summer, this disappears" |

